            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">THE SCIENCE CONGRESS ¶ A SUMMARY ¶ By: T. S. Hall. ¶ [Included in summary of Australasian Association for the Advancement of Science:] ¶  ¶ The writer well remembers a stirring speech made by the late...</supplied>
